msgctxt "Talk01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Even though we all thought it was just\n"
"a child's fairy tale, my brother actually\n"
"dug up the <2.se_co>secret of the hero<3.re_co>.\n"
"<4.so>Now he's so into digging, he'll pretty\n"
"much dig anywhere, anytime.\n"
"\n"
"I'm proud, but I'm also his big brother.\n"
"I can't let him beat me! I'll have to stop\n"
"skippin' leg day and train harder!\n"
"<5.so>As a fellow Goron, of course I'm\n"
"thrilled about it...\n"
"\n"
"<6.so>But as a brother, I'm mostly just worried\n"
"our house is gonna get all dug up\n"
"between the two of us..."
msgstr ""

