msgctxt "Talk02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>My shoulder? Huh?<2.pa>\n"
"...Ah! That's right!\n"
"\n"
"<3.so>Well, the shock of seeing the <4.se_co>secret of\n"
"the hero<5.re_co> dug up totally cured me!\n"
"\n"
"<6.so>The<7.se_co> secret of the hero <8.re_co>is amazing!\n"
"Unbelievable!<9.se_co><10.re_co>\n"
"\n"
"<11.te_si><12.so>Although, it looks just like the shrine we have\n"
"near the city...<13.te_si>"
msgstr ""

